[26/06/2018 07:50:01] <font color="#ffffff">Selvas impenetrables</font>
[26/06/2018 07:50:01] <font color="#ffffff">y altas montañas.</font>
[26/06/2018 07:50:04] <font color="#ffffff">Lugares remotos e inhóspitos</font>
